    "The number of fact-checks per month is shown in Figure 4.",
    "We sampled 500 claims for each response category, leading to a total of 3,000 unique fact-checks to be parsed.",
    "We thereby ensured an equal distribution of outcome labels in the final dataset.",
    "While comparing the two models, we also compare the accuracy of the model with and without additional context.",
    "We therefore run four conditions, GPT-3.5 with context and without context, and GPT-4 with and without context."
